				<div class="param">
					<ul>
						<li>Mascula enters the fray with a new body,<br>piloted remotely from his heart within Laxi.<br>Though pained by conflict to the point that it<br>makes him weep—inasmuch as an android<br>can—he resolves to fight for a better future.</li>
