	<dl><dt
				>
				<span><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/e4c4b6c2cda86984ab5b0997b4b26db62.png"></span>
				<span>Code 03: Rise Generator</span>
			</dt>
			<dd><div>Grants the user a shield and immunity to knockback.<br><br>If the user has Master Control, a more powerful<br>version of this skill called Code 08: Execution<br>will be used instead. In addition to this skill's<br>base effects, Code 08: Execution also grants<br>the user the "Amplified Current" effect.<br>During Amplified Current, the user's standard<br>attacks are buffed and hit more times per attack.</div><div class="skill-detail">Skill Energy Required: 3,840<br>Special Effects:<br>・Knockback Immunity<br>　　Lasts 15 seconds<br>・Shield<br>　　Charges: 1<br>　　Potency: 30% of max HP<br><br><color=#00008B>After Skill Change:</color><br>Skill Energy Required: 3,840<br>Special Effects:<br>・Knockback Immunity<br>　　Lasts 15 seconds<br>・Shield<br>　　Charges: 1<br>　　Potency: 30% of max HP<br>・Amplified Current<br>　　Lasts 11 seconds<br>　　Does not stack<br></div></dd><dt class="skill-cost-wrap"
				>
