						<span>6</span>
					</div>
				</div>
			</dt>
			<dd><div>Grants the user "Master Control."<br><br>If the user has Master Control, a more powerful<br>version of this skill called Code 06: Conclusion<br>will be used instead. Code 06: Conclusion deals<br>damage to surrounding enemies and dispels<br>one buff from each target.</div><div class="skill-detail">Skill Energy Required: 5,570<br>Special Effects:<br>・Master Control<br>　　Lasts 26 seconds<br><br><color=#00008B>After Skill Change:</color><br>Damage: 489 × 6 hits<br>Skill Energy Required: 2,830<br>Skill Energy Required (Shared Skill): 16,668<br>Special Effects:<br>・Dispels Buffs<br></div></dd></dl></div>
