<div class="ability explanation">
	<div class="title">Abilities</div>
	<dl><dt><span><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/83bd9c8302b087a508daec2a8fc9b2cf2.png"></span><span>Debuff Skill Time +20%</span></dt><dd><div>Increases the duration of bleeding and debuff skills<br>that reduce strength and defense by 20%.</div></dd><dt><span><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/e23fa30b574bf7f565547e4d26946c1f2.png"></span><span>Stun Res +100%</span></dt><dd><div>Reduces susceptibility to stun by 100%.</div></dd><dt><span><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/368330649dd4e9c07abc8582ae510ece2.png"></span><span>Last Recovery Ⅳ</span></dt><dd><div>Grants an HP regen buff for 20 seconds when<br>HP drops to 30% (once per quest).</div></dd></dl></div></div></div><div><br></div><div>・The stats shown here do not include increases or decreases due to abilities, and represent the adventurers at level 80 with 50 mana nodes unlocked, not the stats when first obtained.</div><div>・Adventurers with the same name cannot be put into the same team.</div><div><br></div><div>Notes:</div><div>1. For more information about summoning, tap Summon on the in-game footer menu, then select Showcase Info and check the Details tab.</div><div>2. Alberian Battle Royale skins for the adventurers featured in this summon showcase will go on sale and cost fewer items to unlock. Note that some adventurers do not have adventurer skins.</div><div><br></div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.</div>,start_time:1622095200,update_time1621992431